  "body": "### Describe the bug\n\nThis happens on un all versions (including v1.11.0-rc.0), at slot 0 of epoch the time to process block is always 3x-4x higher than other slots\r\n\r\n```\r\nAug-27 02:30:49.504[chain]         verbose: Verified block signatures slot=7189952, recvToSigVer=0.440000057220459\r\nAug-27 02:30:49.494[chain]         verbose: Transitioned gossip block slot=7189952, recvToTransition=0.43000006675720215\r\n```\r\n\r\nfor other slots\r\n```\r\nAug-27 02:31:01.470[chain]         verbose: Verified block signatures slot=7189953, recvToSigVer=0.16199994087219238 | \r\nAug-27 02:31:01.466[chain]         verbose: Transitioned gossip block slot=7189953, recvToTransition=0.15699982643127441\r\n```\r\n\r\nthis could potentially (along with high `notifyNewPayload` time) cause missed attestations due to wrong head being voted by vc\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nthe time to process blocks should be same for all slots\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\n_No response_\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_\n\n### Operating system\n\nLinux\n\n### Lodestar version or commit hash\n\nunstable",
